name: gg.regression.unity.bots.cohtml
description:
An extension package for Regression Games Unity Bots that supports Coherent Gameface (Cohtml).

- To use this package, please also add the `com.coherent-labs.cohtml` package to your project.

- To use this package, please also add the `gg.regression.unity.bots` package to your project from URL `https://github.com/Regression-Games/RGUnityBots.git?path=src/gg.regression.unity.bots#v0.0.30`.
displayName: Regression Games Unity Bots - Coherent Gameface (Cohtml) Extension
